If you are not using the component-installer with zend-expressive, you will
need to add the entry:  \Zend\Mvc\I18n\ConfigProvider::class  to your  config/config.php  class, assuming you are already using expressive-config-manager .  If you are not, add a new global  config/autoload/  file with the following contents:  ?php
use Zend\Mvc\I18n\ConfigProvider;

$provider = new ConfigProvider();
return $provider();
